ms.safi.btsync.dto

Class Folder

  • java.lang.Object
    • ms.safi.btsync.dto.Folder

  • public class Folder
extends java.lang.Object
    JavaBean implementation of a folder's information from BitTorrent Sync.

    An example of a folder's information: 

     
 {
      "dir": "\\\\?\\D:\\share",
      "secret": "A54HDDMPN4T4BTBT7SPBWXDB7JVYZ2K6D",
      "size": 23762511569,
      "type": "read_write",
      "files": 3206,
      "error": 0,
      "indexing": 0
 }
    Author:
    Omeed Safi
